PIN MAPPING - TASK B

Component	ESP32 Pin	Purpose
Button	  GPIO 14	Single button for press detection
LED	      GPIO 5	LED to toggle ON/OFF
Buzzer	  GPIO 25	Buzzer for long press tone
OLED SDA	GPIO 21	I2C Data (Default)
OLED SCL	GPIO 22	I2C Clock (Default)
All GND	  GND	Ground
